Date: 2020-10-29 

Busines Driver nr: 2.002 - User can read reviews for any meal in the catalog

## Status

Proposed (Lukasz)

## Context

In order to facilitated decicion making process on which meal to order, a user can read reviews for any meal in the meal catalog.

## Decision

Providing review system for a meals purchased my users.

## Consequences

Reviews will encurage users to compose own menus, base on recomendations.

**Risk**: Content has to be moderated
